3. Christs third Degree was this, that after He was anointed
                     His third degree, His victory over temptation. by the Spirit, and declared to be the Son of God, then for the Proof of both, He was led by the Spirit into the wilderness to be tempted of the Devil, fourty dayes and nights together;


and in all these Temptations, through his Sonship, and Unction he overcame the Devil, and came away Conqueror: And this was his third Degree in the Church of God, that the annointed Son of God overcame the Devil, in all the greatest, and most grievous Temptations, he could assault him withall.
